dct_description_sm:
Appears in: La Geograpfia di Claudio Tolomeo Alessandrino, Nouvamente tradatta di Greco
        in Italiano ... (1561)

Typical Italian engraved stippled seas and anthill mountain ranges. Later editions
        appeared in 1598 and 1599.
